trans-unit.source: Provides listener-channel notifications from protocol handlers to the worker process framework.
trans-unit.target: 提供从协议处理程序到辅助进程框架的侦听器通道通知。

trans-unit.source: Also enables protocol handlers to access additional parameters, such as the ID of the listener channel.
trans-unit.target: 此外使协议处理程序能够访问附加参数，如侦听器通道的 ID。

trans-unit.source: IListenerChannelCallback is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 中引入 IListenerChannelCallback [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[版本和依赖关系](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: Retrieves data that the protocol manager will pass to a listener channel when the protocol manager is starting that listener channel.
trans-unit.target: 检索在协议管理器正在启动该侦听器通道时的协议管理器将传递给某个侦听器通道的数据。

trans-unit.source: GetBlob is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 中引入 GetBlob [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[版本和依赖关系](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: The data that will be passed to the listener channel.
trans-unit.target: 将传递到侦听器通道的数据。

trans-unit.source: The amount of data, in bytes, that is in the buffer.
trans-unit.target: 中的数据量，字节，这是缓冲区中。

trans-unit.source: Gets the size of the buffered data in the listener channel.
trans-unit.target: 侦听器通道中获取的缓冲数据的大小。

trans-unit.source: GetBlobLength is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 中引入 GetBlobLength [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[版本和依赖关系](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: The size, in bytes, of the data that is in the listener channel buffer.
trans-unit.target: 以字节为单位的侦听器通道缓冲区中的数据的大小。

trans-unit.source: Gets the ID of a listener channel that has to be started.
trans-unit.target: 获取具有要启动的侦听器通道的 ID。

trans-unit.source: GetId is introduced in the [!INCLUDE[net_v35_long](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Versions and Dependencies](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[版本和依赖关系](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)。

trans-unit.source: The ID of the listener channel.
trans-unit.target: 侦听器通道的 ID。

trans-unit.source: Notifies the worker process framework that a new message was received.
trans-unit.target: 通知已收到一封新邮件的辅助进程框架。

trans-unit.source: This method supports the [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: 此方法支持[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/add/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]基础结构，不应在代码中直接使用。
